name: expect
desc:
The Expect package was installed in the LFS temporary tools
directory for testing other packages. These procedures install it in a
permanent location. It contains tools for automating interactive
applications such as telnet, ftp, passwd, fsck, rlogin, tip, etc.
Expect is also useful for testing these same applications as well as
easing all sorts of tasks that are prohibitively difficult with
anything else.
